Pinglet
=======

A server-based instant messaging agent

Description
-----------
Pinglet provides a server-based instant messaging agent which can manage,
receive, transport, and store instant messages for multiple users. Pinglet is
designed to support clients running in web browsers such as mobile browsers or
desktop, or clients running dedicated client programs, and any combination of
these.

